/div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b3e256e-b7d0-4d92-9fef-dff3e5153403\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-da10c858-8713-4154-87cc-1722838739c2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f33a9318-ac0c-44bc-a6d8-c928110197b0\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-047ca65a-428a-4b27-8c95-9e04ab0bca1c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-25c9087e-1e50-4252-a142-0643d678408e\">약해서 아픈 거니까 근육강화를 해야 한다는 주장도 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d8d05269-3399-4aba-8787-adaf15fc60fd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-581d1ce9-3cda-4975-b0d6-da03894c522a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-005138fe-f747-4435-8710-957600afc169\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:225px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-005138fe-f747-4435-8710-957600afc169\", \"src\" : \"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRa5-oY0TdHuDGuIkF5itI0IMyVjastlSWQbQ&usqp=CAU\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRa5-oY0TdHuDGuIkF5itI0IMyVjastlSWQbQ&usqp=CAU\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9a9ec37d-5317-4695-8595-8e55ecffcb38\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8607f295-1c4b-4ea6-b0f3-8377d592fb1a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-72035431-822c-4d6b-a0d4-8a7740e06a1b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-979ec03b-b779-44d8-a4aa-1eb72d11bb8c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0a37b3c8-c50f-4e2b-9539-5eddd043eb20\">어떤 말이 옳은 걸까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6818beb3-ddb7-4a9e-a38e-bf20947419f5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-661a45fd-e1b3-4dcc-ac3c-36d4858ec599\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c36efd15-9771-4144-9ce5-5f9efda34f30\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b7244255-3651-470f-91bd-a7a6ee82ac48\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6f646485-ed04-44f6-8d37-b6ec9209efac\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5a30bdd3-f3c8-4029-b3d4-6681d2032fdf\">정답은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a0d47ddf-c210-49ef-ab1c-33f335ab2044\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bd9d0aed-8af2-4bf0-b1da-6e94f1d5b9dd\">&#x27;근육마다 다르다&#x27;입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ce93a66a-5528-4742-ad7b-23d5690d7fd8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-79e1be90-c5ce-4c6b-be6d-1ebca6e55afc\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-926698c3-a7a5-442c-8786-b71efe9ef177\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8dd600f2-c729-4eee-9752-03296e8dc98d\">근육의 기본 기능은 관절을 움직이는 겁니다. 몸을 움직이는 거죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f18f85a1-14b6-4bd4-8dd9-0eababfb77b6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-098e1dd7-836a-490c-a5d3-67f71e6e0b3e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c7f5a598-aded-47a2-906d-359f8a2b0d8e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-064fcf8e-e951-41fb-a6f4-5d892ea4dc6b\">그런데</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-840635b1-91fa-474b-8c49-0e8b15c6a0eb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0510da19-797b-4a0f-b1b1-e7c92592249a\">어떤 동작을 할 때 하나의 근육만 쓰이는 게 아니고 여러 근육이 함께 작동하게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a572d00c-3c13-49ab-ba1d-bda0ba2fb441\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b45409a2-ee7e-4f49-8e0f-c6e1292335aa\">그 근육들은 &#x27;주동근&#x27;과 &#x27;협력근&#x27; 그리고 &#x27;길항근&#x27;으로 분류할 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f872e15e-fbbb-488f-9dd1-c13b8c019979\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4c24e600-20e1-4064-a269-737130922a9b\">주동근은 특정 동작을 할 때 가장 주요하게 작용하는 근육입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a9cdfae5-42b7-4bf4-80a8-90af235ec24b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3a8ca477-2232-4823-a17b-0d997bf350e1\">협력근은 특정 동작을 할 때 주동근을 도와주는 역할을 하는 근육입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-23dc9538-876a-4b38-9375-9afadba5ae13\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9f08effc-0379-4df4-b259-5b3c51b77f26\">길항근은 특정 동작과 반대되는 방향으로 동작하게 만드는 근육입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2497de78-aca5-45fd-919c-4e931c12ee76\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e47fb579-083c-45ff-aa04-b260ed0dbb70\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-05587e02-10d5-4827-9853-6cdfd394d175\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cee25fa2-05c1-4c9f-9f4e-994c4a7dbc90\">컵을 들어 올리는 동작을 볼까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9e973345-3722-4e38-9f15-c28479492336\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-97caa366-6d7d-4a4b-9399-da014498eb0d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d1ae6421-ef76-4e37-adbb-8662c29f4f4e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d1ae6421-ef76-4e37-adbb-8662c29f4f4e\", \"src\" : \"https://open.oregonstate.education/app/uploads/sites/157/2019/07/1101_Biceps_Muscle.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1584\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1249\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://open.oregonstate.education/app/uploads/sites/157/2019/07/1101_Biceps_Muscle.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6f6191c0-e622-4b79-bb80-51ddec1a1788\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7607543b-cb51-4f67-88f9-d06e6e88fdd6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-27e92c0c-7554-426a-928e-a644ebd4fbc7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6c9f5000-e4e0-46bc-8d5d-2adb764bfb6f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c5dde736-5c7e-46a8-97dd-0453bfd98618\">위 그림처럼 컵을 들고 팔꿈치를 구부리는 동작을 할 때 &#x27;주로 작용하는 근육(주동근)&#x27;은 팔에 알통을 만드는 상완이두근입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-80fe6e5f-036a-453a-9043-3f8611396f44\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-73cc8e40-4359-49b6-83d9-40809388d8f8\">상완이두근이 팔꿈치를 구부리는 동작을 할 때 &#x27;도와주는 근육(협력근)&#x27;은 손목에서 팔꿈치로 이어지는 근육 완요골근이죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1ac2589a-26d6-47c2-b8bd-d9f617845645\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d4d8b6a6-9828-44b0-93f5-81aec9254837\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0f002578-763a-4912-b30a-9190d40775aa\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:416px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0f002578-763a-4912-b30a-9190d40775aa\", \"src\" : \"https://shywmobile.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Agonist-Antagonist-Muscles_Nov-2014.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"416\", \"originalHeight\" : \"317\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://shywmobile.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Agonist-Antagonist-Muscles_Nov-2014.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7a6dc85b-4de1-4122-b514-ea4300d00126\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7aa1b322-f1b6-42dd-aa27-538229d71aa1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-34214c22-de30-4d19-b96b-21a4ec6ded2c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b4f71b7b-5619-4da2-b6d8-b08e34dca684\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2bd69a55-a551-473b-9d66-8447aeaec7d0\">상완이두근은 팔꿈치를 구부리는 역할을 하고, 상완삼두근은 반대로 팔꿈치를 펴는 역할을 합니다. 서로 반대 방향의 동작을 하기 때문에 상완삼두근은 상완이두근의 &#x27;길항근&#x27;입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c70429d4-5462-4dd9-803f-dfab21b30909\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aefe404c-6787-4c65-b00e-c826f883148f\">그런데, 상완이두근이 주동근으로 팔꿈치를 구부릴 때, 뒤쪽의 상완삼두근은 천천히 이완이 되고 길이가 길어지면서 팔꿈치가 자연스럽게 구부러지도록 협조합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-18b9cd71-2825-40ef-b49f-ddd495bb88f6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4256a2af-e8c3-4198-bff0-796666940a57\">상완이두근은 길이가 짧아지면서 팔꿈치를 구부리는 일을 수행하고 상완삼두근은 길이가 길어지면서 팔꿈치를 구부리는 일을 수행하는 거죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8127748c-83ef-4598-b0af-4c53b8b60961\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b5dd2852-5f00-441c-a727-10508feaf023\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d0eede58-fa49-40c5-ba5c-432250461d40\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-90cf9e6c-b5d8-4292-b4ae-af2c9581b5e3\">이와 같이 관절을 움직일 때, 주동근 협력근 길항근이 같이 작용을 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7d2c432c-d82d-4537-b758-6fb0176f9891\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c2b8e2a6-c41a-4603-afdc-e94463c35930\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-11aa2d93-b570-41f9-87b3-5df404a7856b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:288px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-11aa2d93-b570-41f9-87b3-5df404a7856b\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA3MTNfMjg3/MDAxNjg5MjM3MTI0Mjk2.v7gl6W42oZK2xJ6zwYDN84b_UPwESSn76Ya2SEptQFkg.aq_nAO9vysrer4xCEoFmfotx7cTGh90VOFxdacQmY_Yg.JPEG.isuhani/muscle_pain.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"288\", \"originalHeight\" : \"329\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA3MTNfMjg3/MDAxNjg5MjM3MTI0Mjk2.v7gl6W42oZK2xJ6zwYDN84b_UPwESSn76Ya2SEptQFkg.aq_nAO9vysrer4xCEoFmfotx7cTGh90VOFxdacQmY_Yg.JPEG.isuhani/muscle_pain.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA3MTNfMjg3/MDAxNjg5MjM3MTI0Mjk2.v7gl6W42oZK2xJ6zwYDN84b_UPwESSn76Ya2SEptQFkg.aq_nAO9vysrer4xCEoFmfotx7cTGh90VOFxdacQmY_Yg.JPEG.isuhani/muscle_pain.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"288\" data-height=\"329\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3b684cca-eed1-4266-9148-f3240d68c3e2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-734dd96e-5a9c-40aa-bb75-3b7ceb575ba0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9ec1faf3-70ec-468e-b0a0-2218ed52f244\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-48330a8e-1d93-41ca-8884-752b48f043c3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5200e17f-140b-44ed-90c4-359aa366b15f\">근육에 문제가 생긴다면,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0845cd9b-347c-4092-9f53-0223d936a917\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c53be761-360a-43dd-a201-d3eb2df9fd6a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e58f65ac-7153-4041-b845-95890b299fcb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e6b46fa8-e314-40ed-9e68-391fb29e7f25\">주동근은 약화되기 쉽습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e6dcc0b6-4ac0-4528-a148-bd70acd07a3f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e2dc5e41-96f1-422c-aaa0-e4154651b3f2\">협력근과 길항근은 과항진되어 단축되기 쉽습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1363187d-a7c4-4c2c-8146-1ca4a1fde96f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9782aaa9-000a-40bf-bed5-ac97bc230ad0\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8e1c6035-c633-456c-8f91-b7a5f3d1bd89\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-57f35a97-3727-4c98-8a71-0006f678e839\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-311e38f5-854e-4e4f-ad41-641a8c53e1d7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e0da81dc-6a4e-40c9-82a7-0e7b52bfbc5a\">약화된 근육은 강화를,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c5775cb5-adea-4291-ac61-b487253cabb4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dad7d4d0-18dc-4212-8250-06ff4e194ead\">단축된 근육은 스트레칭을 해야겠죠?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2d69338f-4b14-4f30-be9f-b16a8fba4a04\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4e46bde1-5a02-4e16-b121-f3afb350296b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fdbebee6-5dfc-4d7e-b5cf-c47994b136c7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ce2bee7a-b910-470a-8439-d63fbd1b2e9c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a57cc3ed-047a-435d-a884-218daaf242d7\"><span style=\"color:#ff0010;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6a299eb3-3bf1-450c-887e-abd56a3cd8d2\"><b>근육통이 주동근에 발생했다면, 약해져서 문제가 되었을 테니 근육강화를 해주는 게 올바른 치료방법이 되겠습니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7ae6a698-1e46-4a8d-9634-13d6845f3256\"><span style=\"color:#ff0010;\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4b2d0af0-b869-4f7e-bbab-f57b389d65b8\"><b>근육통이 협력근 또는 길항근에 발생했다면, 단축돼서 문제가 되었을테니 스트레칭을 시켜주는 게 올바른 치료방법입니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dd9c1e2d-d838-4d4b-9ac6-94cb3e742417\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-99c03130-1d4d-42d6-a068-3ebc1b63eb8f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-086a0d11-3f76-4942-ae8b-c03fa58b9f2f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:284px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-086a0d11-3f76-4942-ae8b-c03fa58b9f2f\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA3MTNfNDQg/MDAxNjg5MjM3MTQwODUy.cRJ2J1-pA6nhnS3wWEDRl2OSdv1sd9Rj1t1LFjTxiMgg.GYdg9EzsGpSYk4I8v8fArr2YkhiruVEyHCJlxx8fe68g.JPEG.isuhani/muscle_pain_2.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"284\", \"originalHeight\" : \"177\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA3MTNfNDQg/MDAxNjg5MjM3MTQwODUy.cRJ2J1-pA6nhnS3wWEDRl2OSdv1sd9Rj1t1LFjTxiMgg.GYdg9EzsGpSYk4I8v8fArr2YkhiruVEyHCJlxx8fe68g.JPEG.isuhani/muscle_pain_2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA3MTNfNDQg/MDAxNjg5MjM3MTQwODUy.cRJ2J1-pA6nhnS3wWEDRl2OSdv1sd9Rj1t1LFjTxiMgg.GYdg9EzsGpSYk4I8v8fArr2YkhiruVEyHCJlxx8fe68g.JPEG.isuhani/muscle_pain_2.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"284\" data-height=\"177\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource